{"tid":2258970,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"點解美式運動咁唔包容「和局」？","createTime":"2020-10-26T12:37:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-27T00:54:09.000Z","uid":34572,"like":16,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"8f37767bda14d8f589d1d69f16c09bdb26bdde1f","tid":2258970,"uid":34572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T12:37:45.000Z","msg":"大部份運動如果會有機會喺比賽時間內有平手嘅情況出現，喺聯賽制度入面當法定時間內平手就會當「和局」，但美式運動就點都要分到勝負咁，即使係常規賽階段。美國四大聯賽入面，NBA就無限加時賽直到分勝負；NHL就要射點球分勝負；MLB就直頭會唔計落積分榜；NFL雖然叫做比較包容和局出現，但以前四節後打和都要打多十五分鐘加時「黃金得分」，令本身因為比賽模式而較難會平手嘅運動更難出現和局，近年先減到十分鐘加時，但打和嘅機會仍然好細。最搞鬼嘅係當初MLS成立時常規賽打和都係要射軍刀波嚟分出勝負，後來先跟返歐洲足球法定時間平手就計和局。究竟咩因素導致美國人咁唔包容和局嘅存在，一定要打到分到勝負？"},{"pid":"97cf8160d3eb7501c092f077402b63782d83ab62","tid":2258970,"uid":42246,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T12:41:14.000Z","msg":"方便大家嘈交羅<br />\n蠃就蠃輸就輸<br />\n<br />\n打和冇得講 騎撚住垃圾曼/垃圾車"},{"pid":"3e32f5c817aa5f35889d8b374025083113d40c47","tid":2258970,"uid":176282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T12:43:09.000Z","msg":"美國人唔鍾意69"},{"pid":"f0f3de10d83991b1948dc879aafc08863791dd58","tid":2258970,"uid":34572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T12:57:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8afa5fbae70129c7d7af4a4903220f0d4badcfd4","tid":2258970,"uid":189109,"like":28,"dislike":1,"score":27,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T12:59:19.000Z","msg":"因為獎門人唔係美國人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/discover.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89edd9dc9087a23163cdeb0bb7968acae6efec61","tid":2258970,"uid":34572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T13:23:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" c